These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Hobby: puzzles, singing, reading, card-games
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Hobby:reading##1
2. Hobby:card-games is on the far left##1
3. Hobby:reading is between Hobby:singing and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Hobby      | card-games | puzzles | reading   | singing |

