.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, scientific, thriller, martial-arts
Nationality: british, colombian, dutch, turkish
1. Nationality:turkish is between Movie-Genre:thriller and Nationality:colombian##2
2. Movie-Genre:martial-arts is on the far right##1
3. Nationality:dutch is on the right of Nationality:british##1
4. Movie-Genre:adventure is on the left of Nationality:british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | adventure | thriller | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | colombian    | turkish   | british | dutch       |

